{"tid":314264,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《香港獨立論》讀書會","createTime":"2017-07-09T04:47:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-13T17:12:27.000Z","uid":92301,"like":15,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"763811549f85883463f76a072f9cefe3a7878422","tid":314264,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T04:47:00.000Z","msg":"本土民主前線將於7月15日舉行讀書會，討論梁衍華著作《香港獨立論》。獨派過往一直被指欠缺論述基礎，難以說服乃至動員群眾。作為獨派一員，實有必要整理獨立論述脈絡，並以游說港人為己任。<br />\n<br />\n活動名額20至25人，歡迎<span style=\"color: red;\">有興趣人士透過私訊本專頁報名參加。</span><br />\n<br />\n《香港獨立論》讀書會<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">日期：7月15日（六）<br />\n時間：下午3時<br />\n地點：火炭</span>（確認報名後將有專人通知）<br />\n<br />\n（以下為《香港獨立論》簡介，轉載自 <a href=\"http://www.hkaps.com.hk/NewRelease.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkaps.com.hk%2FNewRelease.html&d=Cv9dvMquDalcFwiy0o%2FDRDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=9aa435fd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkaps.com.hk/NewRelease.html</a><br />\n<br />\n// 長久以來，香港主權獨立是一個近乎無人觸及的議題。在開始深入探討該議題前，大部份人已經武斷地否定了主權獨立的可能。本書分為法律篇、古代史篇、近代史篇、當代篇、文化篇及生存篇共六個篇章，嘗試以學術角度去分析香港主權獨立及相關事項。<br />\n<br />\n法律篇以國際法角度探討香港主權獨立是否具有法理依據為開端，再揭示有關的法理基礎與香港是否具有獨立歷史及文化的相關性。古代史篇及近代史篇探討香港是否有異於華夏的歷史觀。當代篇則探討因為沒有獨立主權而在當代面對的問題。文化篇探討粵漢文化之別、香港文化異於華夏及粵英混合的特點。生存篇將假設香港作為一個主權獨立國家，將會面對的生存威脅，以及其他國家面對有關威脅時所採取的應對手段。//）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1929088197345083&amp;substory_index=0&amp;id=1546925482228025\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1929088197345083%26substory_index%3D0%26id%3D1546925482228025&d=Cv9dvMquDalcFwiy0o%2FDRDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=5bfbf2e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1929088197345083&amp;substory_index=0&amp;id=1546925482228025</a>"},{"pid":"2b3df1d65fbd9c51145e76ec687dc58aa4e305be","tid":314264,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T04:52:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4b7843171f6fb7c6dccbee12d9218ff94ff93d3","tid":314264,"uid":112846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T04:57:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5508e238e27425ac4d25d9503912d9275b35290b","tid":314264,"uid":22858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T05:03:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e59b632eb33680af354d5c1c3140c9274cd194d1","tid":314264,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T05:14:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fd925818f27839cc789a42cb5068c1c2c723b58","tid":314264,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T05:51:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb52b4de7e1715fe6cda2e0cccea0d3b76266bf0","tid":314264,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T06:08:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dfd6c33dc30c7b350d9d3a21a92e8387433cda5","tid":314264,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T06:22:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9633087b99850cfef8c62ef66289f98846561cff","tid":314264,"uid":18245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T07:01:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/09/150149_9b06a20be23833f15ea0658fcfb200f8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F09%2F150149_9b06a20be23833f15ea0658fcfb200f8.jpg&h=41ed7dc9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f1907351500bac